#40003
Southern highway~
A small troop of cavalry from the city to the north travels down the highway.
The paved stone road is wide enough that neither you nor they need move aside.
With a searching glance the troop dig their heels in and continue southwards,
ensuring bandits and smaller jealous cities don't stop trade into or out
of the city.
