#40010
Grasslands~
Off the highway grasslands stretch away to the east and south. Miles to the
north the city of Impulzarr dominates the horizon, the largest city for
many thousands of leagues. Out to the west cliffs overlook a vast ocean,
strong winds and crashing waves pounding against the cliff face.
