#40011
Cliff face~
Near the Southern highway out of the city great cliffs overlook a vast ocean
of water. Looking over the cliff face far below you can see waves crash onto
sharp rocks. Even if you survived a fall from this height you'd soon be
pounded into small pieces in the large waves below.
