#40030
Sun Road~
Just visible under the swirling sands the Sun Road leads nort-west, eventually
to the great city of Impulzarr. Once it also lead to lands to the east,
before the desert appeared a century ago. Some say it was an act of a
vengeful god against the arrogance of man, others the work of a mad mage,
whatever the cause the lands are slowly, but surely been buried under the
sands over the course of decades.
