#40063
Wall~
Mounted along the city wall is a large catapult, ready to hurl large boulders
at approaching invaders. The device would be devastating enough on its own,
but some of the boulders have been enchanted by mages in the service of
the city to explode upon impact, greatly enhancing their destructive power.
