#40071
Wall~
The walls around the city are thick and solid rock. Mounted at regular
intervals are holes in the walls for archers to shoot down on targets 
below without exposing themselves to return fire. The walls are smooth
and hard - making it hard for scaling ladders and climbing invaders
to find purchase.
