#40074
Inside Impulzarr~
Standing inside the Southern gates of the city you can hear a hum from 
all the activity, almost as if the city itself was alive. Everywhere 
people are moving - travellers walking wide eyed, citizens shopping, 
guards patrolling, none with any time to stop and talk to the likes 
of you.
