#40076
Watch tower~
Standing high on the watchtower, you can see for miles in every direction. 
To the south the fiery desert, east across the vast plains of fields feeding 
the mighty city. To the west the sea of Stars, stretching to the horizon, 
beautiful, enchanting, merciless. And to the north, Impulzarr. Impulzarr. 
Called the Jewel of the North by it's citizens, less flattering things by 
smaller cities jealous of its power.
