#40126
Wall~
The walls of the city are incredibly thick - 30 to 40 wide. Even with
the magical aid used in its construction the vast walls took decades
to construct. When the walls were started barely a fifth of the area
inside the walls was covered with buildings. Now there is hardly any
space left unclaimed.
