#40128
Wall~
Walking along the wall you come along two young guards in a heated
argument. "No I tell you the Mayflower is THE place to visit" a small
weasly looking guard is telling a tall blonde warrior. "Bah! For
my taste nothing beats The Black Lotus.". "No! The girls at the Mayflower
have the largest ....". The two guards break off their 'discussion'
when they notice you. The tall warrior tells you to move along - unless
you want to be arrested for disturbing the peace - but his red face
spoils the stern look.
