S
#40143
Stores~
Stacked neatly into the small storeroom are all the supplies for this 
portion of the cities walls. Small stores along the wall keep the speed
of any response to attack very quick. Neatly laid out quivers of arrows,
iron rations for the soldiers, sharpening stones for swords, straps and 
a dozen other small items laid out with military precision. Quite an 
arsenal has been packed into the limited space. 
~
400 0 0
D2
~
~
0 -1 40142
S
#40144
Quarters~
Small bunks, barely wide enough to lie in without rolling off the side 
are stacked three high along either side of the wall. A compliment of 
eighteen soldiers maintains each section of wall. Three groups of six 
soldiers, each working two of three shifts during a day for three days 
before a change in duty so none of the soldiers become complacent. 
~
