#40331
Gate Fortress~
Shouts and curses suddenly erupt from below and looking down you can see
two small fishing boats, each with two crew a piece jostling and arguing.
No one could ever accuse the fisherman of fine speech - insults are traded,
ancestory is called in question and suggestions to go perform clearly
humanely impossible acts with small animals are shouted back and forth
until one of the vessels manages to knock over the other and the laughing
guards along the docks turn serious and demand the two boats seperate.
