#40353
Cell~
A hard stone bench to sleep on and a slop bucket are the only 'comforts'
prisoners get in a small cell. The cell has no windows been down within
the fortress. The air is dank and humid, but the cell is only for short
term holding of prisoners caught in the seas surrounding the city, till
they can be shipped to the cities prisons on the mainland.
