#40354
Sea wall~
Mounted along the sea wall is a large catapult, ready to hurl large boulders
at approaching ships. The device would be devastating enough on its own,
but some of the boulders have been enchanted by mages in the service of
the city to explode upon impact, greatly enhancing their destructive power.
Stairs lead down into down, to a passage deep beneath the harbours surface.
